# Manual smoke tests. Run `uvicorn main:app --reload` first and fill in .env.
# Login requests store the session cookie for reuse in later requests.

### Guest login page
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: text/html

###

### Guest login (sets pasha_session cookie)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

password=REPLACE_WITH_GUEST_PASSWORD

###

### Chat page (requires cookie from login above)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat
Accept: text/html

###

### Send a chat message (streams back plain text)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "history": [],
  "message": "Привіт!"
}

###

### Admin login (sets pasha_admin_session cookie)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

password=REPLACE_WITH_ADMIN_PASSWORD

###

### Update persona text
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/api/persona
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Тебе звати Паша. Ти..."
}

###
